Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:12.65,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.7\c&H261A1A&\pos(493.6,474.8)}Plum
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.07,0:00:05.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:09.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm Gerotan! \NI'm making onigiri right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:12.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But don't worry! I'm not planning on making {\i1}that{\i0} your DVD bonus!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.69,0:00:16.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Gerotan is going to eat it himself! \NHe's going on a journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:19.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it everyone, \Njust keep an eye on Cromartie High School for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:22.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Gerotan travels around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:29.42,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\shad0\blur1\c&H3735CE&\frz352.2\pos(490.8,90.8)}Model Gerotan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:25.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and punishes restaurants that are full of themselves despite serving bad food!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:29.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Boo! Boo! What? \NGerotan, can you drive a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:33.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I'm rolling back! \NI'm on a slope, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:37.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I feel sick when I'm moving backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.22,0:00:39.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:43.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Wow, I puked so much! \NIt's a bit of a waste, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:48.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I have plenty more to say about Cromartie High School after this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:54.99,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\shad0\blur5\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(488.89,90.67)}Right now, we’re airing\NSakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:54.99,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\shad0\blur5\fs25\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(201.33,397.33)}We’ll also have an announcement about a giveaway from the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.01,0:00:50.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Also, there will be a gift \Nannouncement from the program!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:53.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You'll get a gift from Gerotan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:54.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,From Gerotan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:57.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.21,0:01:01.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Cromartie High School is said to be \Namong the worst in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.19,0:01:04.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In this case, the worst offender is that fortune slip that brought me misfortune. {???? idk what he means, maybe something from manga?}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.94,0:01:06.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Indeed, it is evil incarnate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:10.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,At Cromartie High School, \NI'm doing my best as always.
